Volunteer Role


Volunteers are encouraged to identify a small business or an underserved woman in their community and capture a photo or video showcasing her work. Along with the visual, write a positive review that highlights her efforts and talents on your social media platforms. This simple gesture can significantly boost her business, while also encouraging her personally and fostering self-confidence.By sharing these stories, we not only promote their work but also inspire others to recognize the value of supporting women entrepreneurs.
